MNIST Digit Recognizer

Draw a digit in the box below and see what the neural network thinks it is! Clear your drawings by clicking the button on the right or pressing any key.

This neural network (784-128-10) was trained on the QMNIST dataset and achieved an accuracy of 97.71% on the testing dataset.
